comments: ["Have been using doglog for a couple years now, it's one of the few apps that I use every single day. I'd be lost without it. There've been a few bugs along the way but they are always responsive and fixed quickly. I especially like some of the recent changes to the events like the drop-down in Medicine to specify the type. It's a lifesaver for multi-carer packs & dogs with health issues, being able to easily create a log of everything to share with the vet is priceless.", "Fantastic app for monitoring your pet's day-to-day life. We had a cat with several health issues and DogLog allowed us to track her health and daily routine easily and effectively. As a result, we were fully prepared for vet appointments with a concise record of her progress and, in turn, the vet could provide more effective medical care for her. Highly recommend this all for any pet owner.", "I like the app as it is very useful to be able to quickly make notes about your dog that will be organised and sorted in a nice way so you can easily go back to it. However a few things could be improved. One thing is the weight curve. The X-axis should be your pet's age, not the number increment of your measurement. If you don't weigh your pet continuously you will not see the slopes of weight gain/loss as realistic in the time dimension.", "The application doesn't allow me to put in the breed of my dog from my profile. Also, all info I inserted got deleted the moment I pressed 'back'button even though I had saved it. I'm deleting this app and finding a working one!", "Great and simple way to track daily activities, as well as medications. I added my dogs exact medication by name (custom) and a few other things specific to her. I decided to get premium so I can view the usual time or day we do certain things, and it has really helped me plan out schedules. It's super easy to use and pretty inexpensive for the information you get access to.", "It's pretty good. I've been using it for about 1 yr now. No ads everywhere and I like that I can filter by event categories. Only problem I have is that I can't delete entries when clicking the delete button. Edit button works but not delete", "This seems like a fairly helpful app and I love that you can share with a pack. I need to monitor blood sugar checks, urine checks, etc. You can make the categories but I really need a graph like the temp feature. I'm using a diabetic pet specific app but it is not stable. If this app grows to that level I would likely pay as the other features seem solid.", 'Any useful analytical data is locked behind a premium fee that does not justify its cost. I can do the same stuff with a free Google form and spreadsheet', 'Perfect for keeping track of toilet routines. Can adapt new icons for other things to track. Very useful', "does exactly what I need it to: helps clear up confusion about who took the dog for a walk and when to help us avoid messy accidents and be aware of our pooch's schedule. the ONE reason this isn't 5 stars for me is the lack of dark mode because this app blinds me every night i take my dog for s walk. otherwise, perfect little simple app.", "Love the simplicity of the interface with the option to add more activities (repeating for a common task or once, like a skunk attack!). Tracking my 11 week old puppy for the past 2 weeks has been extremely helpful. I can see patterns in what times he eats, when we go outside, when he's most likely to have an accident. would be better if you could adjust the time of the event as you are entering it instead of defaulting to current time. Slow app loading screen can be frustrating.", 'Very user friendly interface. Simple to use. The free version has enough features to get started with what appears to be paid for optional extras, which appear useful but not essential. So, you can get started for free and add the extras later, which is nice. Non-intrusive ads too. It has been very useful for us where there are six people plus two dogs in our pack, as we can each log our shared responsibilities and keep track of things. Very useful app.', 'Great app, especially for pups with multiple caregivers so you\'re not constantly texting each other "did you walk the dog before you left?". Intuitive and the simple interface makes it easy to add entries with one hand while being dragged along by over-enthusiastic puppies! The most recent release addressed the only two things I didn\'t like about the app.', "The app is exactly what I look for to keep track of my pet's daily tasks. It has a simple interface that its easy to use. I can easily add more custom items according to my dog's needs. N easily edit items by pushing the task to left. I do like them to record it in current time, so i can calculate walk time, by tapping walk at the start n grooming(cleaning) at the end of the walk. I really hope the data in the app can extracted in later version so it can be presented in doctor's visit. Thanks!", 'Great app for tracking a new puppy\'s every move. So easy to track food, weight, bowel movements, training etc. I love the option to add a photo and "like" or comment on everything. Also easily customize your own buttons (for example, we added "rest" in addition to the "nap" option). Overall great app that we are using as a "pack" with other family members who also have a new puppy.', 'This app used to be perfect. All I needed it was to log food walks and bathroom breaks. However, since my initial download several months ago they have broken every aspect of this. It has gotten to the point where I literally cannot open a dog. I have downgraded to a version of the app from 2018 and have zero issues. I have been sending crash logs regularly in hopes that they fix these problems to no avail. I will be happy to fix my rating once stability is back. Edit 11/4/19: The update to 3.8.13 has certainly fixed my stability issues but it has introduced a new problem. On the previous versions that I was using, when logging something a popup overlay would appear in the center of the screen to select the dog and write any notes. However, now it shows a redesigned full screen page. While I do like the aesthetics of this new page, it now places the dog selection and finish button at the two farthest points from your hand, at the top. With a majority of phone screens exceeding 5.5 inches this makes maintaining the leash complex. A remedy for this could be rearranging the icons to be at the bottom and placing the add a photo button at the top considering that most stabilize photos with two hands making the reach less bothersome.', "This app is the perfect thing that we were looking for. You can create custom recurring events as buttons to reuse. We created ones for sleeping, napping, and crate time. It's really the perfect solution for tracking your dogs habits. Especially great for learning a new puppy's time between eating and eliminating, and bladder control. Thank you for creating this!", 'Been using this app for a year, since shortly after we adopted our first cat and love it! Pretty easy to learn how it works, no obtrusive ads, and a great system for sharing access to the whole family. The only thing that could make it better to me would be the ability to hide certain actions from the "Log Events" screen because I don\'t plan to use some of them for kitty, such as "water" and "pee".', "Update 1/17/23 - Suddenly cannot use the app; it won't open, despite uninsta/reinstall. :( Really like being able to log when she went potty, when she ate, etc - very helpwful if you have ADHD! I also track when we train, go for a walk, any health issues that concern me (e.g. scratching a lot), and when she takes meds. I do wish there were more icons or you could add your own, because I have to repeat them a lot for what I track because there are so few and a limited variety.", "Good but offline issues - If you're out of the house without the internet & switch to a different app, when it goes to reload, it won't, and then when you get back home again & connect to the internet, all the information you added when out the house disappears. Just lost all the walk, pee, poop, drink, eating, treats, vet appointment logs etc I made when I was out. It's very annoying. It could at least store information on my phone to sync up later if I'm offline. I subscribe too.", "Responsive developer. Definitely the best app available. I'm looking forward to the updates. Currently, no ability to enter time of events at initial entry. The log is confusing to read; maybe use the pet photos on the log also? Currently everything looks the same. My Swype keyboard does not work in the app. Maybe allow for a neutral note entry in the log. To keep track of weird occurrences in the pup's life.", "This app has been very helpful to us logging three animals activities between 4 caregivers.  It's simple to use.  My only issue thus far is that when I log an activity it auto-selects every pet, and I have to unselect all, then just select one pet.  I can see where this could be handy for larger packs that do things together. However, I would love the option to set a 'default' selection - I do most activities with just one pet at a time.  Having a preset, or having none selected to start, would save me a couple steps each time.", 'I really love this app. I always end up with orphaned kittens that people bring me, and I often do the record-keeping on paper. This is even smarter. There are options for potty going and feeding. I do wish there was a way to keep records about temperature and body weight and the option to have records for cats as well as dogs. Also, a widget of some of the info would be awesome, too. Over all, it mostly filled the requirement I need in a tracking app.', 'This app allows me to customize events as well as reminders in addition to other already programmed preset options for me and gives a lot of freedom in regards to how many events and reminders you can log at a single time. When I had a question, after emailing, I recieved an answer to my question within half an hour. I may have personally needed help but I would say this app is user friendly and simple to navigate. Very happy with it.', 'Needs a lot of work. Can\'t edit/delete a record once you submit it. Can\'t mark an accident. Have to manually enter the start time twice. No "now" button for the end time to use it like a stopwatch; you instead have to manually input the end time. Default units are arbitrary. (e.g. for "poop" it defaults to a quantity of "miles") Back button on my phone always takes me to the dog chooser screen instead of screen I was previously on. Lack of stopwatch functionality is a deal-breaker for me', 'Was charged for the trial of the premium version. Unsubscribed immediately. Have emailed the developer asking for the money to be refunded. Waiting for a response.', "It's such a brilliant app for keeping records of everything about you dog, especially useful if they are regularly poorly so you can easily track records.", "Easy to add events. Would be better if you could set the time when you're adding an event, instead of having to edit it afterwards. Super for multiple people, nice notification when someone else logs an event. Statistics aren't great. I'd like to be able to visualise the time of day she's going to the toilet, and also in relation to feed time. Would be nice if the information could be exported to csv.", 'It\'s not a bad app, but it\'s crashing all the time for me. I can\'t log anything - I need to try at least 3 times before I\'m able to log anything without the app crashing on me. Also I don\'t understand why they stopped showing the weight history that we had since day 1 of us getting a puppy. For a couple of weeks it started showing only the latest logged wright event, but now it says "No events" logged - it\'s very upsetting :( I have the latest version of the app, but it still doesn\'t work.', "It's good but the only downside is there doesn't seem to be an undo button would be a nice feature. EDIT - There is a way to delete! Thankyou support team that makes the app so much easier to use! 10/10! Really useful for keeping track of toilet training and I love the fact you can add other activities 👌 would absolutely reccomend this to my friends with pets particularly puppies", "Great app, but there is no way to edit the log entries. I made some mistakes and also want to switch the way I document the heats, but I cannot go back and edit the old entries. I would make new ones but then I would have the entry doubled, since I can't delete the old ones. I like the possibility of creating custom log categories.", 'Edit: Thanks for responding! I updated my rating. Looking forward to the new version :) . . . I wish you could delete events, edit events, and add more than three pets (I use it for my ferrets too). I also wish there was a "vet" option. Other than that, it serves its purpose and we\'re able to communicate when we bring her out and feed her with everyone in our household.', "This app is AMAZING. A few small QOL things, but completely offset by how helpful it is. I'm tracking so many things for my cat who has some issues I need to keep an eye on, and this is MUCH easier than notepad. But...... Huge banner ad appeared at the top of the app today. It's very obnoxious. Still very worth it, and I 100% support them getting some income for it. I donated through the link. But maybe if you're going to go the ad route, you could have a paid ad free version? Still 5*, but 🤞?", "Update: They fixed the crashing issue really fast! I love this app because its really easy to log what you need to. It has a lot of features to use. However my main reason for getting an app like this is to be able to predict what time my dog will go potty. I was hoping the app would do this for me, but you have to pay $40 a year for it! I can't spend that much a year. I get that the makers of this app need money too, but I wish they would let you buy individual features without a monthly cost.", "I really like this app so far. The only thing I'm not happy with is in the profile feed. There are some fields like breed and food brand that I would like to add for my pup, but you seem to have to select from a dropdown. Having a rescue mix, my breed is not on there and my food brand also doesn't appear in the list. I would like the option to either select Mix or Other. Otherwise a freetext input field would be much more useful.", "Though not a dog owner, this app is the best I've found so far for tracking feeding and other necessary reminders for caring for our cats. I would love to see this expanded to include other animal breeds!!! My only downfalls, again not a dog owner but a pet owner who needs to keep track of pet health, are that some of the profile details don't have the option to be written in (food, breed, etc.). Also, I would like to be able to delete some of the activities that I do not use (i.e. outdoor activities). Again, this app would be PERFECT if it included other animal types as well!", "This app has helped me so much with tracking everything my new puppy. It had made potty training so much easier! One of the best free apps I've tried!", "Exactly what we needed for our new puppy. Especially if one person is taking over responsibilities during the night, morning, work hours, etc., we can easily see what happened and when to anticipate the upcoming events.The only thing we wish we could figure out is how to share reminders with the whole pack. Right now it looks like it's only visable to the person creating the reminders, but we are using this feature to set upcoming vaccinations, etc. and want the whole pack to get the reminders.", 'Briefly, overall, it gets the job done. But important things just arent options. We play ALOT more then we walk but there is no button for, "play". Each picture needs to be really small which sucks. I take many pics that I cannot send. There\'s no place in the feed to write a simple written update. I have to send 2 long texts during the day to give a more detailed update. The caption with each activity has to be under 7ish words. I could write a lot more. Definitely could be better IMO...', "It's a nice app with a clean interface. I like being able to track things about my puppy's health. However, the biggest downside to me is that I can't seem to find a way to edit or delete log entries. I wanted to add notes to a log after I made it, but I haven't found a way to edit it and I can't delete it and recreate the log with notes. This seems like a major feature that is completely missing. No options to work around this defect as far as I can tell."]

title: Duddu - My Virtual Pet Dog
description:
Let us introduce you Duddu, our new dog! He is a super nice dog who lives in a wonderful world full of fun and adventure. Become a part of Duddu’s everyday life and build a true friendship with your new virtual pet.

• As a new pet owner, you are responsible for feeding, putting asleep, entertaining and looking after your own dog in his lovely house. In addition, you will have to take care of your scout dog in the wild as well!

• Oops, Duddu needs doctor's help! Welcome to the animal hospital full of doctor games to give your dog the treatments he needs. Appoint him to the right vet’s office to solve a problem with fleas, stomach, leg, virus or wound. You can also pick some medicinal herbs and cook potions at the outdoor fireplace.

• It’s time for a spa adventure! Have fun in the pool or sauna with Duddu’s pet friends and enjoy preparing smoothies or coloring mandala in the cutest pet beauty salon. 

• Visit every corner of Duddu’s world and all of his friends, too. Take him on vacation to the sunny island with a cosy hammock and coconut palms. Customize your own pirate ship and teach Duddu different tricks at the dog school. Enjoy dancing in the club, exercising in the gym, painting and doodling in the gallery or playing drums and piano in the music centre. Have fun exploring the colorful world where the Sun goes up and down whenever you want.

• Play over 30 different mini games and earn some coins or other goods. Have fun playing Bubble Shooter, Solitaire, Archer, Pirate Battle, Brick Breaker, Block Puzzle, Treasure Island, Moto Racer, Fruit Connect, Space Explorer, Hen Farm, various cooking games and many others. Go shopping and buy some unique pieces of furniture, food and clothes or customize your pirate ship and your house.

• Complete daily challenges to learn about the dog’s habits and become a master of achievements to get some extra rewards. Check your mailbox everyday, you may find a surprise gift from a special friend.

This game is a guaranteed fun for people of all ages. Taking care of a pet gives you a sense of responsibility and loyalty. All you need to begin the fun journey is your own Duddu dog!

This game is free to play but certain in-game items and features, also some of those mentioned in game description, may require payment via in-app purchases which cost real money. Please check your device settings for more detailed options regarding in-app purchases.
The game contains advertising for Bubadu’s products or some third parties which will redirect users to our or third-party site or app.

This game is certified compliant with the Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA) by FTC approved COPPA safe harbor PRIVO. If you would like to know more about the measures we have in place for protecting child privacy please see our policies here: https://bubadu.com/privacy-policy.shtml .

comments: ["I played this game in my old time and installed this one more because this is my first favorite game ever. And we can go all around and friends house 🏠 ,hospital,and also play many games and we didn't want network also i really like this game 💕❤😘🥰😍🤩🥳❣️❤🧡💛💚💙💜🖤💞💓💗💖💘💝💟", 'I love this game its so fun that u can play with ur pet and all kinds of stuff!', 'This is very best 👍game to play because my little 🤏sister loves to play in mobile and she learn too much best things from this game and I am also soo glad for this game to play with my little 🤏 sis', 'It is awesome but I do not like when everything is locked but I will still give five stars and I love this game', 'Highly recommend! I got this game for my young son but I genuinely enjoy playing it with him. The best thing was that the ads were not overly persistent nor distracting. There is a lot to do, but we still ended up purchasing the extended version because it was a great deal, especially compared to most other games.', "Wow excellent pet game. Great for kids. 3 year old didn't get it, but 5 year old got the basics down. I played it myself and it's really well made. I love all the activities that are possible with the pet vs other games that only let you do basics.", 'Cute,BUT!!..it\'s so laggy & "weird". Like I played the exact same game on my friends\' phone,& she finds little gifts/diamonds & foods everywhere & gets the option to double her score after EVERY game. I only got the option every other game,& I\'d always lose the money I\'d "worked hard" for(?),~so I\'m uninstalling.', "I really like duddu he's so cute. It's fun to play and it's suitible for kids. We can go to dog club, dog school, music centre, art gallery. And we can go to friend's house even ofline! And we can learn how to play songs in the music centre! I've learn the song 《Twinkle Twinkle little star》 and we can go outside shower, sleep, eating and go toilet. It's just like camping. Love the game🥰🥰🥰", 'This game has more opportunities than the cat version and I ❤ it', "It is so much fun to play! My brother and I play it all the time, and it wasn't boring at all! You can visit your friend's house, the gym, club and also the school! It is like a life simulator but cartoon version. Recommend this game 100%! Hope you'll make games like this in the next generation 😘😍", 'My children love it!! Interactive environment, clickable. So fun! Many variation of games. The flaw is only the adds. But not too annoying though.', "I think the game needs some more upgrade because the pets needs to do what we want it to do is not supposed to tell us what it want to do and we're supposed to be able to control the friends as well so they could have slumber party and all those stuff and we're supposed to have kitchen things that we like frying pans that we could fry the eggs and stuff so it's three stars", 'Lovely game and easy too', 'I only have this game to play the mini games which I like except ludo is a total fix. Sometimes the computer will get 3 sixes in a row in the same go and then whatever number it needs next just to catch me to prevent a win. Very infuriating.', "This game deserves 5 star this is very best game.. this game is very exploring for kids as there are many games and works to do, That is amazing that we can also change the things.. My little son have fun to play this game and there are also some things that is my son explore and learn... So i like to give it 5 stars i hope later you'll must update and add new games.. in it.🙂🙂🙂.", "Would you help me to hack Duddu right now??? I don't need to update Duddu anymore because I don't like his new look but I like the old look, same as my Little Pony. Duddu is a great dog and I'm always taking care of him... I am changing his different outfits I bought for him. One mistake I ever made... I was in level 72 but I went back to level 1. I am in level 44 now. Duddu And I Were Best Friends Forever!!! Thank you, Bubadu!!!!!", 'It should contain siblings and a park to play with friends', 'The game is pretty good , however everytime he call\'s for me like a notification ive been recieving a couple of notifications from him like " please be back " and it was annoying me even tho i kept playing this game for like hours , and the most annoying part is that you can\'t mute or off the notifications you got from this game. title: Panda Games: Pet Dog Life
description:
Welcome to the Pet Dog Home! Are you ready to begin a cozy house life with your dogs? Adopt dogs, take care of them and play with them!

ADOPT DIFFERENT DOGS
14 adorable dogs of different breeds and colors are waiting for you to adopt. Each dog has its own personality! Adopt your favorite dogs and live in the pet dog home with them! There are surprises in every corner of the cabin!

TAKE CARE OF PET DOGS
The dogs' day starts with a delicious breakfast! Add dog food, and feed them well! After playtime, give your dog a nice bubble bath! Don't forget to monitor their health and treat the sick ones!

DRESS UP CUTE DOGS
Now, open your closet and dress your dog in cute clothes! First, let's wear a cape for your dog and then pick a nice bib for it. Last, put on a cozy little hat for your dog! Done! Your dog looks even cutter now!

PLAY WITH DOGS
There are so many toys that you can play with your dogs: frisbee, swing, and more! Play with your dogs in any way you like at the pet dog home! This will bring you closer together. Try different fun mini-games and exercise your brain while playing!

Download Panda Games: Pet Dog Life and spend some fun time with your dogs in the pet house!

FEATURES:
- 14 cute dogs available for adoption;
- Feed, bathe, dress up and take care of your dogs;
- Explore the Pet Dog House: living room, bedroom and playhouse;
- Plenty of dog toys: tennis, swing and frisbee;
- Many fun mini-games to play with your dogs;
- Supports offline mode！

About BabyBus
—————
At BabyBus, we dedicate ourselves to sparking kids' creativity, imagination and curiosity,and designing our products through the kids' perspective to help them explore the world on their own.

Now BabyBus offers a wide variety of products, videos and other educational content for over 400 million fans from ages 0-8 around the world! We have released over 200 children's educational apps, over 2500 episodes of nursery rhymes and animations of various themes spanning the Health, Language, Society, Science, Art and other fields.

—————
Contact us: ser@babybus.com
Visit us: http://www.babybus.com

title: Lovely Pet
description:
Dogs are very lovable, sweet, and charming animals. They are our stress reliever, our companion, and our loyal best friends. We play with them, we feed them, and we share bed with them. Having pets offers us lots of benefits - in physical, emotional and even in mental health. 

Lovely Pet helps you simulate what it is to have a dog at home while earning rewards. It is like having a real dog. Your everyday tasks are just simple - feed him with his favorite delicious food, give him water when thirsty, play with him, and make him sleep when tired.

You can redeem your points with PayPal, GCash, or mobile recharge.

Note: All games, tasks and rewards given by DigiWards are not affiliated with Google Inc. The offers are solely sponsored by DigiWards. All rewards are not Google products; and or do they have any association with Google.
summary: Take care of the pet, collect points, and earn rewards

comments: ['The game have many features which are really unique. At first, everything went well, and we received everything on schedule. However, compared to factories and buildings, the time it takes to acquire fresh land is excessive. Otherwise, everything is fine. Ad is totally unrelated to the game. Good game all around. Your hard-earned money goes into the piggy bank, and you must purchase it before using it or you will lose the $75. Are the game designers counting on us to keep purchasing it repeated.', "Need some improvement on this game! This game is one of my favourites. I adore the vibrant candies. The application's creator just updated the music and added new candies. Although the new music is equally excellent, the old music truly fit the game and was a good fit for this particular game. If there were a way to go back to the previous music, that would be ideal. And it crashes right away if I watch any videos for more manoeuvres. When a level is almost complete I am so happy.", "Honestly I love the app. It's helpful to learn the basics before getting a teacher. What I don't like is how sometimes it just refuses to hear the notes. I've seen other people complain about that so it's not just me. Like I will have my keyboard turned up to max volume and it just refuses to hear the notes. Other than that lovely app. Edit: Turns out it's the sounds of the app interfering with the piano so if you just mute the app it works perfectly.", "Overall performance is better after update. I'm not even sure if I should because of the confusing level-up screen. When I play an advertisement, I don't always receive the prize that the advertisement promises to offer me, and frequently, the game will end and return me to the home screen on my phone. levels keep stalling. When I reach level 19, it will stall. I can restart the game to start at the beginning of a level and receive offline awards as if I had never played.", "The gameplay is amazing and challenging, the controls are easy to learn and best of all, no intrusive ads. Instead of the game forcing you to watch ads every time you DO SOMETHING (like most mobile games) it tries to lure you in with sweet deals. Now I'm not saying that you can't make a quick buck, but it's much better than having to watch an intrusive ad. The devs care, not only about the money it makes, but they care for their players more.", "Overall I really like this so much from the beginning. Really excellent game overall. You don't have to pay to have a nice experience, and the graphics are excellent. Since there has been no resolution for more than a month, I was unable to fully enjoy the game. I can see every single detail because I am a game developer. I can say that this game has heart even though some of the story components are lifted directly from more well-known franchises. It's different from the typical first-person.", 'This is a great game! This is my favorite game. But lots of bugs, major updates have broken the app. The most recent update has made this app almost unusable on my phone (funtouch os). The double-tap to lock screen functionality keeps getting turned off by the os due to malfunctioning of the app. similarly the os keeps switching back to system launcher after every few taps on the home screen. Extremely annoying. Please fix ASAP.', "The App looks great but I still don't understand what the registered security code is all about. title: Fancy Dogs - Puppy Care Game
description:
Dogs have never been this fancy before. Join us on our fun journey of collecting cute puppies and turning them into the fanciest dogs ever seen in this new free cute dogs game in the history.

Play addictive match 3 puzzles to collect cute puppies and costumes. Can you find all dog breeds and costume sets? Dress up your fancy dogs and show them off to your friends and family. Go find out more about the secret life of pups.

Features:

- Another fun adventure created by the minds behind Fancy Cats, suitable for any dog lover out there, from boys to girls, from young to old.

- Prepare for the ultimate cuteness, with a huge selection of fancy dogs: 20+ different dog breeds with distinctive personalities. Collect them all: fabulous Chihuahuas, adorable French Bulldogs, gentle Dalmatians, and many more such as the Beagle, Rottweiler, Pitbull, Chow Chow, Staffordshire Bull Terrier... We are missing your favorite dog breed? Don’t worry! We plan on adding many more in the future such as the Bichon Frise, Labrador Retriever, Great dane, Cocker Spaniel, Shih Tzu, Pomeranian, Doberman Pinscher and of course the Pug.

- Watch as your pups play and talk to not only each other but also to you. Wake them up as they are sleeping and feed them with treats. Name each of your new pet with adorable names such as Molly, Bailey, Daisy, Max, Fluffy, and Bella; and start bonding with them as soon as possible.

- Pet your little puppies and see their reaction. Each puppy will have their own reaction.

-  What is a pet without a toy? A huge selection of toys for your fancy dogs to play with. Watch your puppies make funny faces as you give them different toys. Have your cute dogs chase a robot squirrel. Or give them a giant donut to eat. Can you guess what happens?

- Raise and take care of the fancy dogs from cute little puppies to full blown grown-ups. Each pup just can't grow up fast enough.

- Spoil the cute dogs with a huge collection of costumes. Let your fancy puppies become firefighter, wizards, police officers, etc. The possibilities are endless.

- 300+ different addicting match 3 puzzles, with a wide variety of difficulty for you to either relax with or challenge yourself. The more challenging, the bigger the prizes. Each match 3 puzzle was designed with different fun mechanics in mind. Each puzzle rewards you with a star, which you can use to open chests containing new prices.

- 9+ dog parks with beautiful backgrounds, which you can even upgrade to make them even fancier.

- Take pictures of your pups and share them on social media to show off how stylish you can make your pups.

- Show off your puppies with other players, and make some new friends along the way. Can you make your pups be the cutest of them all? 

- Come back every day for your free reward.

- One of the best girls games / mom games / puppy games free for dog lovers.

- The game is entirely free, containing in-app purchases. Aphmau fans will love this for sure!
summary: Collect 20+ different dog breeds with distinctive personalities.

title: My Puppy Friend - Cute Pet Dog
description:
If you are a pet lover, these cute puppies would definitely melt your heart!

Your love and care could make the little ones' life different! Take them home and feed them with delicious food. Or give them a shower to wash off the dirt. A stylish makeup pairing with a chic outfit will help the pets stand out in the show, which would award you with a lot of decorations and take the puppies' home up a notch! Parkour, seek out the bones…many fun activities are ready to blow your mind!

Features:
- 6 cute puppies that melt your heart
Life gets a whole lot more interesting if you take these little cuties home. 
- Collet loving hearts to open the Show where you may get decorations
Each time you complete a mini game, one heart would be awarded to you. With 3 hearts, you can join the Show and win the decorations.
- Earn coins and exchange them for nice items
Take the challenges with your pets to earn as many coins as you can and exchange them for food, outfits and other nice things.
- Fun-filled mini games work well with the amazing scenes
Have fun with your doggies in such gorgeous scenes and wonderful activities.

About Libii Game:
With over 600 million downloads and growing, Libii is committed to creating innovative games for kids. We'll keep working on establishing a good relationship with both parents and their children and bringing a healthy, happy atmosphere for them.
Visit us: http://www.libii.com/
Like us: http://www.facebook.com/LibiiGame
Contact us: Got any ideas? Suggestions? Need technical support? Please feel free to contact us 24/7 at WeCare@libii.com

Need You Know:
This app is totally free to download and play, some basic items are also free to use, but some additional items need you to purchase and pay to unlock. Therefore, if you do not want to use these items, please turn off the in-app purchase in your settings. Thanks.

comments: ["Its an OKAY game it's just that there are too much ads especially on the top and i can't focus when there is a Google ad up on my screen. And there is literally NOTHING that is for free except for the ugly clothes and i hate that! Please considering lessing up the ads because it's getting really annoying now. I uninstalled it because of the ads. I know that you have to have ads because people want their ads to be in your game BUT no one will like your game if ads keep popping up and annoying us.", "It's very interesting game. I like it very much. I like most to ready my pet for shows. And to win Parkour and earn coins. First time I don't know how to play. But after many struggle I become expert in this game. Please install this game and play u will definitely like it.", "It's just kinda boring. All you do is endlessly do the same things taking care of a dog. I can imagine this getting old really fast. Maybe it's because I'm 10, and maybe this was made for toddlers. I don't know. It's boring, that's all. Maybe if there was more to do, and it wasn't so...toddlerish? I think a toddler would really enjoy this though! There's also cute graphics. Reccomended for ages 3-6 for me. I think I don't like it cause I'm a little too old. title: Old Friends Dog Game
description:
Welcome to Old Friends Dog Game, where love never grows old! Create your own dog sanctuary in this heartwarming pet rescue simulator. Rescue adorable senior dogs and uncover their life story as you shower them with love. Decorate with cute doggy decor, bake scrumptious dog snacks, and experience the joy of helping cute senior dogs live out their golden years in the best way possible. 

Inspired by the real life pet residents at Old Friends Senior Dog Sanctuary, these cute dogs have heartwarming stories and personalities that you'll uncover as you rescue them and provide the care they need to live their best dog life!

Awarded Gold winner at the 2022 NYX Awards, a finalist for Pocket Gamer's Game of the Year, and a Webby honoree for Social Impact in Games, this cute dog simulator is a must-play!

Gameplay:

❤️ Meet the town residents and rescue cute senior dogs. Help them live their best life by fulfilling their needs and ensuring their happiness. As you feed, pet, and play with your dogs, their love and loyalty grows.

📘 Choose how the story unfolds. In this dog simulator, you pick the path for each dog's story! Unlock multiple chapters for every cute doggy you rescue.

💒 Customize your dog sanctuary and make it a haven for your dogs. Decorate indoors and outdoors with cute doggy decor that will make your dogs feel right at home!

🧁 Bake lip-smacking treats for your beloved dogs, ensuring they never go hungry.

🧣 Dress up your dogs in cute pet outfits! Each dog has adorable accessories that you can earn.

🐕 Give your dog sanctuary the personal touch - feature a custom profile, a unique avatar, and a gallery of cute photos of each dog!

**********

Old Friends Dog Game is developed and published by Runaway.

This game is free to play but does contain some items available to purchase for real money. If you run into any issues while playing or you have any suggestions, please reach out to us at support@runaway.zendesk.com. OLD FRIENDS DOG SANCTUARY™ is made by Runaway Play.

comments: ["Absolutely loving the game so far! I'm relieved it's not another match 3 or merge 2 games, and really is about taking care of old dogs and managing the sanctuary. I've seen the game's advert for a long time, I regret not playing it sooner. But better now than never I guess! Only thing is the game keeps crashing on me occasionally while loading a new scene (ex; getting a new dog, loading livestream, .etc) I love the game and I want to support the funding, I'd appreciate a smoother experience. :')", "I played the game a while ago and recently reinstalled it, but now it won't even let me past level one. Everytime I try to stream it just makes the screen go black, and nothing happens. I've tried everything to fix it, reinstalling again, restarting my phone, even went online to try and find an answer. Love the game, just wish I could get further with it.", "I absolutely love this game! It's adorable, and I haven't experienced any bugs (I have played for about a month now). Though, for the Dog Blog, there are limited color options, which, as someone with bright green hair, is a little saddening :( Aside from my dramatics about hair color, I recommend everyone give this game a try! It's so customized, and each dog has their own favorite treats and toys, which is so fun to memorize. I love this game!!", "This game is really amazing and I love the style so much! I really like the game because it's supporting a real life senior dog sanctuary too! But last 3 or 4 days I couldn't get in the game because i got a message about some kind of error and I tried everything to get rid of it but it hasn't been working so far. I got pretty good progress there so it's going to be sad if i lose it. I don't know if its a game error or its like that for someone too but I hope it gets fixed soon!", "Very Cute very relaxing it's really wholesome too! But, I've been having issues lately When I stream the screen becomes black and the music keeps playing and I can't go to the next level because my first time of streaming is glitching I've been having Issues with that so whatever you could do please Fix it....", "First things first, this is not a game you will play for an hour straight. More like a few minutes at a time. Gameplay is fun though. Little thing I mentioned pre-edit, So basically my progress reset, (It has been fixed now.) Devs should probably look into what caused that. Also I don't know if the message I sent to tell them it was fixed worked? All in all, great game, great devs. (What caused the game to reset though?)", "A awesome friendly game where you get to experience adventures and journey with these adorable dogs and the amazing artwork! I love this game. It's just heartwarming. And there is so much more potential to expand apon! The fact that it was based on real dogs and experiences is also amazing. You get to read snippets of real-world inspiration the further you progress.", "This is THE BEST chill/idle kind of game I've ever played. There's so much to do! You are always getting rewards constantly, even past the early game. There are only ads very rarely, when you want to increase your rewards. The dogs are so sweet and have personality that you uncover through their individual story lines. You'll fall in love. I had this game ages ago and left it like I always do with mobile games (I'm fickle lol) and this is the ONLY game I missed so much I had to come back again!", "This game is fun but I got stuck on the streaming stage Everytime I tried the screen would go black to the point I just left and rejoin the game and when I kept trying it took my stuff but never worked if u could see if it's a bug please update Soo it doesn't happen to other people", "it was almost an amazing game, except for the fact that it was lacking in furniture and decoration aspects. it's fun caring for the dogs, but i wish i could put more furnitures. there's so many furniture blueprints, but i cant craft becuz the materials for good furnitures are so hard to get. i wish we could buy materials from donations, or we could get from streams. idk. im quite unsatisfied witht the reward rn", "This make me cry so much. I love idle games. I love that this is based off an actual doggy sanctuary with the actual doggies and with pictures of the actual doggies attached. I'm sad and happy and my heart melt. Some lags and bugs are experienced and the game crashes too. But i just love the concept of this game. Good strategy to make ppl adopt senior dogs and cry cause they're gone too soon", "It's really great especially for dog lovers! I Love it a lot and especially that it's also a real sanctuary.. It really makes me wanna donate now :( but my parents do not allow me sadly... I hope some people will still donate :) definitely will recommend some friends to play this..!", "Old friends dog adventure is such a fun game where you care for older dogs and play the challenges! You get to choose what to say and there's even a dog blog! Definitely would recommend.", 'Sancuaty names could be more customizable(wanted to name mine after my old pup, Timber.) But otherwise, The game is amazing. The graphics are great. The dogs are adorable. And I love the hat for Mack.', 'Absolutely what I was looking for in a game, perfect with little to no ads and with very reasonable microtransactions! Would recommend', "Very cute! I would love if the game would emphasize the importance of identifying dog-friendly costumes that won't bother dogs vs coatumes that will make them uncomfortable all day, but overall its super fun 👍", 'This Is such a heartwarming game, I love how simple are the interactions with the dogs. I love the little stories that they include of the dogs adapting to their new home. Amazing game!', "THIS GAME IS THE ACTUAL BEST! BAGEL IS SO CUTE MACK IS SO CUTE AND LEO IS SO CUTE,there's so many things to do!Decorate your sanctuary,collect new dogs,and it's all so much fun I love the theme and design of the game and how they're based on real life senior dogs!I wish I could meet them in real life!I was quite sad when I found out they only sold the merchandise in USD cuz I'm from the UK but seriously if I could I'd give this game a million bigillion stars out of a million biggilion stars!☆", "I am only on 3rd level, and I think it is really fun, cute, and great for a dog lover. I do find it a bit repetitive, but that will probably change over time. I olso do think Runaway's other games are really good too. If you delete their games, your progress will not be saved, though.", 'This game is so cute and entertaining! The dogs are adorable. Even the situations where almost nothing is going on it is really fun. Just baking food or cleaning the house just makes you feel happy and calm. I love this game and I really recommend this game for all dog lovers! ❤️', "It's such a cute game about dogs and don't love a dog for its age love it forever no matter what because old dogs are cute too and in the game you can unlock cute dogs like mack and bagel and Leo there so adorable doesn't matter how old a dog is love lasts for eternity I love Leo Babs and Captain Ron too runaway pls update maybe fix the bugs? Not asking for much ty the bug is it takes a bit to load and sometimes when I try saving a picture it says contact support game kicks me out any way to fix", 'I feel good playing with old friends, . I recently had to start a new game over because old friends got accidentally erased , I was devastated. Old friends helps me cope with losing my old friend scrappy. He was my everything, he passed away not long ago he was 16 and so loved. Thank you old friends for reaching out and I was very excited to hear from you. Thank you old friends.', 'This game is just so adorable, and the fact that it is based on real life dogs just makes it 10 times more interesting and unique! Love it, keep up the great work. ( I also totally recommend!)', 'This game is adorable and I love the concept of it. It is so cute and so fun, and i love that the dogs each have the personalities of the real pups. And favorite treats and toys. Babs is my favorite pupbso far hehe Ten stars from me!', 'Ohh, they have fixed the problem, the game is really wonderful, and very innovative, please I recommend you download it and give it a try', "So far, it's a really fun game! However I wish furniture was cheaper and there were more coupon codes. But overall, it's really good!", 'I love this game but my account got restarted and when i just wanted to play i was in the start again i dont know to get my stuff and my progress back please help i dont wanna start again.I still have the furniture that is needed coupons. But the ones i crafted is gone and the progress of the dogs are gone and i only have mack again', 'Edit: After 2 years of playing this game, it has become quite dull. The events are all repeats from the years prior... I already have all the rewards from the bake-offs, so why even participate? I have been at the max level for probably a year now. Not much to do after completing the stories. I have 3 senior rescues myself (2 dogs and 1 cat), so this game is perfect for me. I recently applied to vet school and want to focus on old animals. This game is everything I want out of life!!!', 'One of the first times a mobile game has truly felt like a game. Love oozes from every millimeter of this experience. Even the ads are non-intrusive, and from what I understand completely optional. Highly recommend!', 'Game has reset on me twice, erasing all my progress. The first time I used recover to get back to my original game. The second time it reset, I tried to recover my original game, but only the two previous reset games appear, making me start with zero progress. If this is not fixed, I will never play this again.', "Super cute and makes me feel better about playing mind-numbing games that get me nowhere. The only complaint I have is that the app randomly restarts sometimes after an ad video. Also, videos have been unavailable for me all day so I can't get Mack his chicken flavoring 🥹", "Love the premise behind the game and was enjoying playing it. The dog message requests bugged out with no images and did nothing when I clicked on them so I rebooted the game and it lost all my data :( I'm scared it will happen again.", 'This game is so much fun, and although you have to work very hard, the dogs are soo cute. Most relaxing game ever!', "It is amazing there's lots of adventures the dogs are so cute but the best thing is getting more of the dog's stories.", "This is a cute game and I enjoy it but I can't progress past the streaming part as the screen just goes black.", 'So far this is super cute and fun. a little bit slow, but really heartwarming and relaxing.', "Cute little game. I haven't closed it since download because I'm mildly afraid of missing things when my attention differs, but that's the only issue and isn't even really one! The whole app is so fun and adorable that I can't keep my hands off of it 🙈", "I don't know why it's taken me so many years to download a wholesome game about dogs. So far into the game, it's easy to follow, lovely story and beautiful graphics. If you love dogs and want causal gameplay, this should suit you:)", "Love this game; it's so nice and wholesome! There has been issues with my progress resetting, but whenever that happens I breeze through the intro sequence then contact support through the game's settings, and they fix it in like a day. One thing I really wish the game had though is the ability to replay cutscenes, because the stories are just really cute.", 'Amazing game 10/10 never run iut of things to do, great asthetics, you just get to chill with good puppers, no annoying ads without consent and great atmosphere, highly recommend']

title: Pet Perfect - Puppy & Dog Care
description:
Recognized as one of the Best Apps of 2022 by Google Play🚀

Embark on a Journey to provide the best care to your Doggo 🐶.

Get easy to follow, daily schedule of activities, curated by experts.

As a dog parent, we know you are tired🤔 of wasting time looking for info according to your pets age & breed. It’s hard to keep a track of their daily key activities like feeding, walking, bathing, brushing, etc. Many a time you can’t remember the vaccination & deworming dates📅. Don’t know what steps to take for your doggo’s perfect upbringing? Because your pet can’t tell you what they need! We seldom seek the opinion of experienced Pet Parents & Veterinarians. But in reality, we need one place to learn all the best dog health care practices.

Pet Perfect is your one-stop companion for everything you’ll need to make the most of your furry friend. The best companion for your pets, curated with love and passion😇.

🐾Pet Journey- feature provides pet parents with step-by-step tasks on every stage of dog life according to your dogs age and breed.

🐾Pet Engagement - Have fun with your furball with our vivid range of perplexing dog sounds🔉

🐾Vaccination & Deworming Tracker - Get automated reminders for your dog's vaccination and deworming dates with just a single tap. 💉

🐾Dog Community - Get your queries resolved by Experts and Veteran Pet Parents & make new friends who share our love of doggo🐕.

Check our website here:- https://www.petperfect.in/

Also, do follow our Social Media Handles:-

Instagram:- https://www.instagram.com/petperfect_ig/

Facebook:- https://www.facebook.com/petperfect2021

P.S. Currently, we support the following pet types: Dogs
summary: Complete Daily Routine - Trainings, Information, Reminders, Community, Records

comments: ["I have been using the app for a few days. This has a cute and simple interface. There are useful information and also a community where you can ask your questions. However, the major problem I faced was when I opened the app recently the app first page didn't show up instead it wrote formatexception:unexpected character and asked to tap to retry..after too many tries still the pages don't show up.", "Thanks for this 😊 i am very happy to use this this app helping me to train my dog very easily thank you very much this is very interesting I can easily use this just love it keep ti up 🤠😉 but now I having too many problems like i can't read all the guide he says that I need to get a subscription whyyyy", "It's an Amazing App. It is a perfect solution to my pet parenting problems. I used to forget health check-up and vaccination date. I used to blame myself for delays. But Pet-perfect allows me to automatically manage my health records. The Premium is worth it. Thank you pet perfect for making my life easier.", 'I love the app, so much good information, and I especially love the reminders. As someone with ADHD, it makes life 10x easier to know that this app keeps track of EVERYTHING I need to do for my puppy 🥺 My only suggestion is a way for families, or couples to connect pet accounts so that they can keep track of the care together!', 'very very helpful and informative instructions are really helping to raise a puppy without any hesitation', 'Really good app especially for new pet owners.would absolutely recommended it.at first it blew my mind', "My name is Denita and our Instagram handle is @_.labradore._ We're totally in love with this pawsome app. Indeed a great help for pet parents especially first timers. It is so easy to access the guides given in the app, you can find the solution of almost every concern through them. The vaccination reminders are also of great help. Really appreciate the hardwork of the creators and the team behind it. One thing that I would like to have changed is that we can only ask one query in a day.", 'Your app is perfect except that when I try to get into app it shows " UPDATE APP". Which I couldn\'t, I tried uninstalling and reinstalling the app again, which was of no use. NOTE: THIS APP DOESNT HAVE AN UPDATE IN PLAYSTORE. How do I update it?', "My name is Shikha and our Instagram handle is @eskiego I want to say that I love this app. It makes pet parenting so easy with all the activities reminders, vaccination and deworming reminders and a wide range of guides which help to understand our furbabies' behaviour perfectly. In today's busy world, this app is the most necessary thing so that you do not miss out anything and take care of your fur baby in the best possible way.", "Really very good app, but as the name says, I think it's missing other types of pets, at least cats, in addition to dogs. Please take as a suggestion to update this wonderful app. I have two cats and my puppy, so I miss information about my cats as well 😻🐶", 'Amazing App. THE PERFECT APP FOR PET PARENTS. I love the app.❤ In the App, there are Health records, Activity reminders, Expert Guide and the most important PET COMMUNITY where u can ask Questions and get Answers from EXPERTS. Thanks for the Amazing App.🤗', "My Name Is Priya and our Instagram handle is @thejessijr i want to say that i love this app. It makes pt parenting easy with all the activities and reminder vaccination and deworming reminder and a wide range of guides wich help you find Your Furbabys Behaviour perfectly. In today's busy world this app is the most nessessary thing so that you don't miss out anything and take care of you pooch in best possible way ✨❣️", "amazing app... just an additional suggestion..personalized diet chart timings and suggestions is something I felt missing according to my dog's health, weight and age.", 'Very easy to navigate through, and super informative!!! A must-have for all pet owners.', "Love the detailing in the app. One stop solution for all my pet needs. It used to be such a hassle earlier and now we just gotta get on the app and it's done. Thank you devs.", "Amazing app for both new and experienced pawrents! It's gold out there. Just what I had been looking out for since I got blessed with my first furbaby. 🐶🌻", "It's a very informative and a helpful app, keeps me updated for my pet's vaccines and medications if any. Totally recommended.", 'I am delighted to say that the information on each points are very useful and helpful for the parents of a GSD. Many many thanks for sharing such an excellent and informative post. With best regards. Asit Kumar Sau LL.B, WBPS. Deputy Superintendent of Police, Retd. Advocate Belur Bazar, Howrah. West Bengal.', 'This is a very informative app, with all the related information needed like vaccination info, health-related info, etc. This app is highly recommended to pet parents.', 'Amazing app with all the features details & best part is all the guides are very scientific & personalized for my dog 🐕', 'Very useful app for a pet owner. but irritating notifications many times a day.. had to block from phone settings', 'Amazing app for pet parents. Amazing and informative guides helps me a lot . The interaction of pet parents helps to clear all the doubts and problems. ❤️ Would give 5 stars to them', 'I\'m not able to sign in. It shows a message in snackbar saying "Sending OTP failed!"', "Every pet owner must have this app this is an very good application to maintain our pet record's as well as the knowledge given in this application is very good.", 'Good app the wikis are helpful vaccination schedule really eases things very helpful for modern pet parents like me', 'Best for may dog breed . try this app best app forver . 😍😍', "It's an amazing app....one stop shop for all your needs.", 'Informative, Helpful and Reliable. 👍🏻', 'Whole profile have created then so many times app will updated ... So bad Experience...not gud', 'best experience with this app', 'very helpful app for those who raise pets at home। thank you.', "It's very helpful App for Pet Owners , it intimates our duties of taking care of our pet's .", 'Very nice app and platform to discuss the dog related issues with a very good community', 'This app is very good app i can read all about puppy care and ask any question in this app i just want to give more stars but there are only 5 great app goo and install now', 'after updating feeling difficult in searching to update vaccination , deworming', 'One stop destination for all the pet products', 'Very great app. Best for any pet parents!', 'Useful & easy to understand', 'I have paid for this app but it is still showing upgrade', 'Nice App must download if you have a Pet.']

title: Bigo Live–Live Stream, Go Live
description: BIGO LIVE allows you to live-stream your favorite moments, make friends from all around the world, and watch 24/7 live stream to kill boredom. We have over 400 million users around the world. RECOMMENDED TO PEOPLE WHO: - Want to watch live streams and interact with hosts in real-time - Enjoy online music concerts - Like chatting with people from around the world - Enjoy watching gaming live streams and discussing strategies - Are interested in becoming an influencer by showcasing your talents - Like to support others who work hard for their dreams - Love luxury goods WATCH LIVE STREAM Millions of talented broadcasters, dancers, singers, foodies, comedians, and more. LIVE VIDEO CHAT / VIDEO CALL No boredom. BIGO LIVE can match you with locals around you or with people from all around the globe. LIVE VOICE CHAT / DROP-IN AUDIO CHAT The space for casual, drop-in audio conversations—with friends and other interesting people around the world, similar to Clubhouse. LIVE PK (LOL) Broadcasters with the most points will win, and losers will be punished. Dare or not? ;) LIVE GAME STREAMING Go live stream or watch other’s live-streaming popular games, such as PUBG, World of Warcraft, Minecraft, GTA, Fortnite, Dota 2, Among Us and more. GO LIVE Get followers, gain fans, receive gifts, make friends and become an idol to others. SAY HELLO: Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bigoliveapp Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/bigoliveapp Twitter: https://twitter.com/BIGOLIVEapp YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/bigoliveofficial Any feedback? Please contact us at feedback@bigo.tv
summary: Watch fun live streams, chat with people from around the globe, and get rewards!
